ed="T" n="0728c01"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0728c01"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000020588">淄州</placeName><persName key="A001708">慧沼</persName>傳（<persName key="A009215">大願</persName> <persName key="A009083">塵外</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0728c02"/><persName key="A001708">釋慧沼</persName>，不知何許人也<ptr target="#n589"/>。少而警慧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g590"/>，始預青<lb
ed="T" n="0728c03"/>衿<ptr type="glossary" target="#g591"/>，依于庠序，誦習該通<ptr type="glossary" target="#g350"/>。入法修身，不違戒<lb
ed="T" n="0728c04"/>範，乃被時諺<persName key="A001708">沼闍<anchor xml:id="beg0728sgsz5"/>梨<anchor xml:id="end0728sgsz5"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g127"/></persName>焉。次攻堅于經論，善<lb
ed="T" n="0728c05"/>達翻傳。自<persName key="A000294">奘三藏</persName>到<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，恒窺壼奧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g592"/>。後親<persName key="A001019">大<lb
ed="T" n="0728c06"/>乘基師</persName>，更加精博。及<persName key="A001358">菩提流志</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000042324">崇福寺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0728c07"/>譯《大寶積經》<ptr target="#n593"/>，<persName key="A001708">沼</persName>預其選，充證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>，<placeName key="PL000000048606">新羅</placeName><persName key="A001179">勝莊<lb
ed="T" n="0728c08"/>法師</persName>執筆，沙門<persName key="A009215">大願</persName>、<persName key="A009083">塵外</persName>皆一時英秀，當代<lb
ed="T" n="0728c09"/>象龍。于時<persName key="A009217">武平一</persName>充使，<persName key="A002111">盧藏用</persName>、<persName key="A009070">陸景初</persName>總<lb
ed="T" n="0728c10"/>預斯場。中書侍郎<persName key="A002459">崔湜</persName>因行香<ptr type="glossary" target="#g594"/>至<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042324">翻經院</ref>，<lb
ed="T" n="0728c11"/>歎曰：「清流盡在此矣，豈應見隔？」因奏請乞<lb
ed="T" n="0728c12"/>同潤色<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g70"/>新經。初，<persName key="A001708">沼</persName>證義<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g54"/>於<persName key="A001470">義淨</persName>譯場，多所<lb
ed="T" n="0728c13"/>刊正，訛言舛義，悉從指定，無敢踰制。後著<lb
ed="T" n="0728c14"/>諸疏義，號<persName key="A001708">淄州沼</persName>也。</p>
